The paper deals with the automatic detection and recognition of periodic pulse train signals using a multi-stage process based on spectrogram edge detection, energy projection, and classification. This work involves the use of machine learning classifiers and their performance evaluation. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.SD (Sound), cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
